data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET! Buyers financing fell through.  NO HOA!!! This exceptional property perfectly blends comfort and style.  Step inside and experience generous living spaces designed for relaxation and entertainment. Four bedrooms provide plenty of room for family, guests, or even a home office.The sparkling pool is perfect for a refreshing dip on hot summer days. This home offers easy access to schools, shopping centers, and parks, and Orlando is only 45 minutes away, and steps from the main highway of Florida such Turnpike, ST-50, US-19, US-27 and INT-75,ensuring a convenient lifestyle. It's an ideal setting for creating lasting memories and enjoying a blissful lifestyle. Schedule a showing today!
